@ncw The  support for`diffie-hellman-group-exchange-sha256` is now added to ssh library [here](https://github.com/golang/crypto/commit/57b3e21c3d5606066a87e63cfe07ec6b9f0db000). But as it states in the code:

> the key exchange algorithms diffie-hellman-group-exchange-sha1 and diffie-hellman-group-exchange-sha256 are not included in the default list

Rclone needs to opt in the support. Any idea how?
